20refueling%20aircraft%20%26quot%3Bwent%20down%26quot%3B%20in%20Iraq%2C%20the%20US%20military%20announced%20Friday%20evening.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20second%20unidentified%20aircraft%20was%20involved%20but%20landed%20safely.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20status%20of%20the%20refueling%20aircraft's%20crew%20is%20unknown.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20US%20military%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-air-force-boom-operators-keep-calm-inherently-dangerous-job-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKC-135%20refueling%20aircraft%3C%2Fa%3E%20involved%20in%20Operation%20Epic%20Fury%20has%20crashed%20in%20Iraq%2C%20US%20Central%20Command%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Friday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCentral%20Command%20is%20aware%20of%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20US%20KC-135%20refueling%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20command%2C%20which%20oversees%20US%20military%20operations%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20incident%20involved%20two%20aircraft%20operating%20in%20friendly%20airspace%20in%20support%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-us-general-rundown-opening-days-iran-attack-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEpic%20Fury%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20aircraft%20%26quot%3Bwent%20down%26quot%3B%20in%20western%20Iraq%2C%20while%20a%20second%20unidentified%20aircraft%20landed%20safely.%20The%20aircraft%20loss%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20due%20to%20hostile%20fire%20or%20friendly%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20CENTCOM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20marks%20the%20fourth%20American%20aircraft%20loss%20since%20the%20start%20of%20Operation%20Epic%20Fury%2C%20the%20Pentagon's%20name%20for%20US%20operations%20against%20Iran%2C%20nearly%20two%20weeks%20ago.%20Just%20days%20into%20the%20war%2C%20CENTCOM%20announced%20that%20three%20American%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-aircraft-losses-iran-israel-kuwait-several-warplanes-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EF-15E%20Strike%20Eagles%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20downed%20by%20friendly%20fire%20over%20Kuwait.%20The%20aircraft%20were%20lost%2C%20but%20all%20six%20aircrew%20members%20were%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-survival-training-that-kicks-in-after-pilot-is-down-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeject%20safely%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20KC-135%20Stratotanker%20is%20an%20Air%20Force%20asset%20that%20supports%20the%20broader%20joint%20force%20by%20refueling%20other%20aircraft%20%E2%80%94%20including%20fighter%20jets%2C%20bombers%2C%20and%20cargo%20aircraft%20%E2%80%94%20in%20notoriously%20complex%20midair%20refueling%20operations.%20It's%20essentially%20a%20flying%20gas%20station%20that%20executes%20fuel%20transfers%20at%20high%20speed%20with%20aircraft%20in%20close%20proximity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20KC-135%20typically%20carries%20a%20three-person%20crew%20%E2%80%94%20a%20pilot%2C%20co-pilot%2C%20and%20boom%20operator.%20The%20status%20of%20the%20crew%20is%20not%20known%20at%20this%20time.%20CENTCOM%20said%20rescue%20operations%20are%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-us-military-refueling-aircraft-went-down-in-iraq-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773355959000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b343ada96e437d6eb83f30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-us-military-refueling-aircraft-went-down-in-iraq-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20Central%20Command%20said%20the%20incident%20that%20brought%20the%20plane%20down%20occurred%20in%20%26quot%3Bfriendly%20airspace%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20not%20the%20result%20of%20friendly%20or%20hostile%20fire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbaker%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-us-military-re