ESeveral%20months%20before%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantir-moves-headquarters-miami-florida-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPalantir%20moved%20its%20headquarters%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Miami%2C%20an%20entity%20with%20ties%20to%20the%20company's%20billionaire%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falex-karp-bio-palantir-ceo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%2C%20Alex%20Karp%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20put%20down%20roots%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20Hibiscus%20East%20LLC%20purchased%20a%20home%20on%20Miami's%20San%20Marino%20Drive%20for%20%2446%20million%2C%20according%20to%20property%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20several%20of%20Karp's%20other%20properties%2C%20the%20LLC%20is%20registered%20in%20Delaware.%20It%20is%20connected%20to%20an%20attorney's%20office%20in%20Manchester%2C%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20and%20an%20accounting%20office%20in%20Bedford%2C%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20both%20of%20which%20appear%20on%20documents%20from%20previous%20real%20estate%20transactions%20that%20are%20linked%20to%20Karp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nearly%2010%2C000-square-foot%20newly%20built%20home%20sits%20on%20San%20Marino%20Island%2C%20one%20of%20the%20exclusive%20Venetian%20Islands%20in%20Biscayne%20Bay.%20A%20YouTube%20video%20of%20the%20home%20posted%20by%20listing%20agent%20Dina%20Goldentayer%20showcases%20the%20property's%20waterfront%20and%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldentayer%20declined%20to%20comment%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20Representatives%20for%20Palantir%20and%20an%20attorney%20for%20Karp%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Palantir%20announced%20it%20was%20moving%20its%20headquarters%20to%20Miami%20from%20Denver.%20The%20company%20has%20not%20revealed%20publicly%20why%20it's%20making%20the%20move.%20Before%20setting%20up%20in%20Denver%20in%202020%2C%20Palantir%20was%20headquartered%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20c