ng%20we're%20looking%20for%20in%20a%20value-priced%20sofa.%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Flaherty%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhite%20glove%20delivery%20is%20free.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EShipping%20can%20take%20two%20to%20three%20weeks%20for%20in-stock%20models%2C%20and%20six%20to%20eight%20weeks%20for%20custom%20orders.%20Quince%20provides%20free%20white%20delivery%20and%20will%20assemble%20the%20sofa%20in%20the%20room%20of%20your%20choice.%20Flaherty's%20sofa%20was%20ready%20in%20about%2010%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20risks%20involved.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EQuince%20is%20a%20direct-to-consumer%20brand%2C%20so%20you%20can't%20test%20the%20Sierra%20in%20a%20showroom.%20Once%20it's%20in%20your%20home%2C%20returns%20must%20be%20initiated%20within%20seven%20days%20of%20delivery%20and%20are%20subject%20to%20a%2015%25%20restocking%20fee%2C%20which%20varies%20from%20Quince's%20typical%20year-long%20return%20period.%20The%20sofa's%20frame%20has%20a%20lifetime%20guarantee%2C%20but%20other%20defects%20aren't%20covered%20by%20a%20warranty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fquince-sofa-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQuince%20Sierra%20Performance%20Velvet%20Curved%20Arm%20Sofa%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e343a2e9-f00d-41e3-98a3-1f537d9884d0%5C%22%3EBest%20modular%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Sactional%20is%20designed%20to%20grow%20with%20you.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Lovesac's%20modular%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118263707ri-20%26h%3D1f2b751ec04786ac6c1478fd894b59a83019cbe42881b1da386ec04d33f1a9e0%26postID%3D69b0785f7b9cac572eba6756%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-sofa%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.lovesac.com%252Fsactionals%252Fbuild%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E