y%20can%20feel%20overwhelming.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Sactional%20is%20delivered%20in%20a%20veritable%20mountain%20of%20separate%20boxes%20containing%20seats%20and%20sides.%20Assembly%20involves%20putting%20large%20legs%20into%20holes%20at%20the%20base%20of%20a%20seat%20or%20side%2C%20then%20sliding%20the%20other%20end%20of%20those%20legs%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bshoe%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wooden%20square%20with%20holes%20that's%20kept%20on%20the%20floor%20to%20keep%20the%20seat%20or%20side%20in%20place.%20Metal%20clamps%20are%20used%20to%20hold%20separate%20pieces%20together.%20Feeling%20confused%3F%20Lovesac%20created%20helpful%20videos%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmkUP5dmDxy8%26t%3D290s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunboxing%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMFrbbFDz-lk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eassembly%3C%2Fa%3E%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c23ba5f-702b-46a4-81cd-6928bd6aeb48%5C%22%3EBest%20sleeper%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20mattress%20is%20top-notch.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118263707ri-20%26h%3D4c7ae4c0e08305dfc70a44ea5b291fda5074d7d1ee6c9580d8b039f2373f58ad%26postID%3D69b0785f7b9cac572eba6756%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-sofa%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.westelm.com%252Fproducts%252Fshelter-sleeper-sofa-h1891%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShelter%20Sleeper%20Sofa%3C%2Fa%3E%20comes%20in%20just%20one%20size%2C%2080%20inches%2C%20with%20a%20queen%20mattress%20inside.%20Made%20with%20high-density%20foam%20and%20gel-infused%20memory%20foam%2C%20the%20mattress%20is%20designed%20to%20contour%20to%20your%20body%20and%20keep%20it%20cool%20on%20warm%20nights.%20A%20sturdy%20metal%20frame%20prevents%20the%20mattress%20from%20sagging%20if%20you%20sit