xtremely%20tight%20weave%20that%20resists%20pet%20claws.%20Note%20that%20Sixpenny's%20fabrics%20are%20all%20non-toxic%2C%20with%20no%20coatings%20to%20make%20them%20stain%20repellant%20or%20more%20durable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223794%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sixpenny%20Elias%20sectional%20in%20Garden%20Berry%20blue%2C%20sitting%20on%20a%20blue%20and%20red%20Turkish%20rug%20in%20a%20finished%20basement%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66390aabec0c696569015c67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222845%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKaplan%20chose%20a%20cotton%20linen%20blend%20fabric%20and%20it's%20held%20up%20very%20well%20to%20cat%20scratches%20and%20daily%20use.%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrepare%20to%20wait.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20can%20take%20up%20to%2012%20weeks%20to%20get%20your%20custom-built%20piece.%20Threshold%20shipping%20is%20free%2C%20but%20Kaplan%20recommends%20paying%20%24100%20extra%20for%20white-glove%20delivery%2C%20since%20the%20sofa%20has%20a%20large%2C%20heavy%20kiln-dried%20hardwood%20and%20plywood%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20expensive%20but%20worth%20it.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPrices%20vary%20by%20fabric%2C%20but%20Kaplan's%20sofa%20currently%20costs%20%246%2C049%20before%20tax%20and%20delivery.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20held%20up%20beautifully%20to%20many%20movie%20nights%2C%20dog%20visitors%2C%20cat%20cuddles%2C%20and%20naps%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20within%20your%20means%20to%20shop%20there%2C%20I%20couldn't%20recommend%20it%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fsixpenny-furniture-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESixpenny%20Elias%205-Piece%20Sofa%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c884ca57-74ac-454c-a651-5c4ae4e6e186%5C%22%3EBest%20Cloud-couch%20dupe%3C%