0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbenchmade-modern-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBenchmade%20Modern%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219145282-b131-453c-b0aa-89453aa629b5%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20small%20spaces%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20apartment%20friendly.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Burrow's%20popular%20mid-century%20Nomad%20comes%20in%20a%20range%20of%20configurations%20%E2%80%94%20from%20loveseats%20to%20five-seat%20corner%20sectionals%20%E2%80%94%20depending%20on%20the%20selected%20upholstery.%20Each%20has%20a%20modular%20design%2C%20with%20individual%20sections%20that%20can%20be%20removed%2C%20added%20to%2C%20or%20rearranged%20to%20suit%20the%20most%20unique%20spaces.%20All%20sofas%20feature%20a%20built-in%20USB%20charger%2C%20and%20the%20back%20cushions%20can%20be%20reversed%20with%20a%20plain%20or%20a%20tufted%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20so%20many%20ways%20to%20style%20it.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBesides%20the%20configuration%2C%20you%20can%20choose%20the%20leg%20finish%2C%20block%20or%20slope%20arms%2C%20and%20upholstery%20in%20performance%20flatweave%2C%20performance%20chenille%2C%20top-grain%20leather%2C%20or%20performance%20velvet%20upholstery.%20Writer%20Jada%20Wong%20tested%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118263707ri-20%26h%3Dcfdfcde1ef71be56ccd60cf7088f86aceb0d54e54fab494cd6892ab59f7bb72b%26postID%3D69b0785f7b9cac572eba6756%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-sofa%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fburrow.com%252Fproducts%252Fnomad-plus-leather-king-sectional%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENomad%20Leather%20King%20Sectional%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20black%20leather%20with%20walnut%20legs%20and%20says%20it%20showed%20no%20signs%20of%20scratches%20or%20tears%20after%20two%20years.%20The%20seat%20cushions%20initially%20felt%20too%20padded%20but%20squished%20down%20nicely%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20black%20leather%20sofa%20with%20a%20coffee%20table%20in%20front%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b08b84441e48aec3a1d9c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Burrow%20Nomad%20is%20a%20modular%20sofa%20with%20mid-century-inspired%20styling%20that%20has%20a%20small-space%20friendly%20scale.%3Cp%3EJada%20Wong%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESetup%20can%20be%20tricky.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Nomad's%20modular%20pieces%20ship%20to%20your%20door%20in%20individual%20boxes.%20To%20assemble%2C%20you%20put%20two%20seats%20next%20to%20each%20other%2C%20then%20secure%20them%20with%20a%20metal%20latch%20between%20the%20seats%20and%20on%20their%20underside.%20However%2C%20Wong%20says%2C%20the%20metal%20latches%20were%20hard%20to%20find%20and%20secure.%20One%20person%20had%20to%20use%20their%20body%20weight%20to%20force%20the%20seats%20flush%20against%20each%20other%20while%20the%20other%20fumbled%20with%20the%20latches.%20Most%20customers%20said%20their%20sofas%20came%20together%20in%2020%20minutes%2C%20but%20it%20took%20Wong%20an%20hour%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20She%20also%20notes%20that%20the%20Nomad's%20underside%20is%20covered%20in%20a%20thin%2C%20cheap%20black%20fabric%20secured%20with%20staples%20and%20that%20she%20accidentally%20ripped%20the%20fabric%20while%20securing%20one%20of%20the%20latches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fburrow-leather-couch-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBurrow%20Nomad%20couch%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a133ab5-3bf3-4469-a9ac-adc1c7e36ab7%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20pet%20parents%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20pet-friendly%20fabrics%20is%20a%20snap.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20Insider%20Reviews%20senior%20home%20editor%20Jaclyn%20Turner%20was%20searching%20for%20a%20sofa%20that%20she%20%3Cem%3Eand%20%3C%2Fem%3Eher%20dog%20could%20enjoy%2C%20Joybird%20made%20it%20easy.%20The%20brand's%20site%20offers%2090%20upholstery%20options%2C%20which%20can%20be%20easily%20filtered%20by%20category%3A%20velvet%2C%20pet-friendly%2C%20stain-resistant%20Safeguard%2C%20sustainable%2C%20Greenguard%20Gold%20certified%2C%20and%20Pantone.%20Turner%20chose%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118263707ri-20%26h%3D3ba79626a4181f6ffd9ecc16a136447b6596d2ee0375a016b40ee725b08db82d%26postID%3D69b0785f7b9cac572eba6756%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-sofa%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fjoybird.com%252Fsectionals%252Fwilder-sleeper-sectional%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWilder%20Sleeper%20Sectional%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Premier%20Sea%2C%20a%20durable%20Sunbrella%20fabric%20that%20%26quot%3Brepels%20liquids%20and%20stains%2C%20and%20resists%20any%20snags%20from%20my%20dog's%20nails%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20It's%20also%20available%20in%20many%20configurations%2C%20including%20a%20standard%20sectional%20and%20a%20slightly%20less-deep%20apartment-size%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20plush%20and%20dreamy.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Wilder%20Sectional%20includes%20a%20chaise%20and%20has%20deep%2C%20plush%20seats%2C%20overstuffed%20back%20cushions%2C%20and%20a%20bed%20that%20glides%20out%20from%20the%20main%20frame.%20Joybird%20offers%20two%204.5-inch%20mattress%20options%3A%20standard%20foam%20and%20an%20upgraded%20Tempur-Response%20Memory%20foam.%20Turner%20chose%20the%20latter%20and%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20thought%20I'd%20see%20the%20day%20when%20I%20had%20a%20good%20night's%20rest%20on%20a%20sofa%20bed%2C%20but%20I%20awoke%20with%20no%20aches%20or%20pains.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20aqua%20colored%20sectional%20sofa%20with%20throw%20pillows%20and%20a%20blanket%20on%20top%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b17b014d65ec517529cfff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20addition%20to%20comfortable%2C%20modern%20silhouettes%2C%20Joybird%20offers%20dozens%20of%20pet-friendly%20and%20stain-resistant%20fabrics%20that%20stand%20up%20to%20daily%20life.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStill%2C%20it%20could%20be%20better.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere's%20no%20space%20for%20storage%20and%20the%20chaise's%20orientation%20is%20not%20reversible.%20The%20Wilder's%20deep%20bench%20seats%20%E2%80%94%20which%20make%20feet%20dangle%20when%20you%20lean%20back%20%E2%80%94%20may%20not%20be%20ideal%20for%20older%20people%20or%20those%20with%20mobility%20issues%2C%20and%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20slide%20forward.%20Joybird%20sent%20a%20non-slip%20pad%20to%20keep%20it%20in%20place.%20The%20upholstery%20on%20the%20large%20bench%20cushion%20also%20ripples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESofas%20qualify%20for%20premium%20in-home%20delivery.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20costs%20%24179%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20every%20penny.%20The%20Wilder%2C%20which%20measures%20123%20inches%20and%20includes%20a%20chase%2C%20is%20bulky%20and%20heavy%2C%20so%20Turner%20appreciated%20that%20a%20crew%20carried%20it%20into%20her%20home%20and%20helped%20with%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fjoybird-sleeper-sofa-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoybird%20Wilder%20Sectional%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed889192-d058-4860-9d50-b3bf3be2b8b5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20sofa%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20best%20sofa%20is%20the%20one%20that%20fits%20your%20needs%2C%20aesthetic%2C%20and%20space.%20Measure%20your%20room%20carefully%20%E2%80%94%20including%20doorways%20and%20circulation%20paths%20%E2%80%94%20and%20consider%20how%20the%20sofa%20will%20relate%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20furniture%2C%20says%20interior%20designer%20Mina%20Lisanin%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.minalisanin.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EML%20Interiors%20NYC%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThe%20right%20scale%20helps%20the%20room%20feel%20balanced%20and%20functional.%26quot%3B%20Additionally%2C%20consider%20how%20many%20people%20will%20regularly%20sit%20on%20the%20sofa.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20family%20of%20two%20a%20pit-sectional%20is%20likely%20too%20large%20for%20your%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20design%20historian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Falessandrawood.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlessandra%20Wood%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BLikewise%2C%20if%20you%20constantly%20have%20more%20than%20four%20people%20sitting%20in%20your%20living%20space%2C%20you%20will%20want%20a%20sectional%20or%20an%20extra-long%20sofa.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUpholstery%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESofas%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecome%20in%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20materials%2C%20including%20cotton%2C%20canvas%2C%20linen%2C%20velvet%2C%20and%20leather.%20When%20deciding%20on%20upholstery%2C%20think%20about%20who%20will%20be%20using%20the%20sofa%20and%20how.%20%26quot%3BA%20household%20with%20kids%2C%20pets%2C%20or%20frequent%20guests%20will%20need%20something%20more%20durable%20than%20a%20sofa%20in%20a%20formal%20sitting%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Lisanin.%20%26quot%3BNatural%20fibers%20like%20cotton%20and%20linen%20can%20be%20beautiful%2C%20while%20performance%20fabrics%20offer%20added%20durability%20for%20everyday%20living.%26quot%3B%20Performance%20fabrics%20are%20treated%20to%20resist%20stains%2C%20says%20Wood%2C%20and%20allow%20them%20to%20easily%20wipe%20off.%20%26quot%3BMachine-washable%2C%20slip-covered%20sofas%20are%20also%20a%20dream%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20adds%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20you%20can%20quickly%20launder%20the%20entire%20thing%20and%20make%20it%20look%20brand%20new.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrame%20construction%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EQuality%20sofas%20are%20crafted%20with%20a%20solid%20hardwood%20frame%20and%20hand-tied%20springs%2C%20says%20Wood%2C%20who%20advises%20shoppers%20to%20steer%20clear%20of%20inexpensive%20couches%2C%20which%20can%20feature%20lower%20grade%20materials%20like%20manufactured%20wood%20or%20plastic.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20often%20made%20with%20inexpensive%20frames%20that%20can%20crack%20or%20wobble%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Wood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECushions%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Seat%20cushions%20should%20feel%20sturdy%20when%20you%20sit%2C%20which%20is%20why%20you%20want%20to%20avoid%20low-density%20foam%20fills%20that%20sag%20very%20quickly.%20%26quot%3BHigh-density%20foam%20or%20down-wrapped%20cushions%20help%20maintain%20shape%20while%20still%20feeling%20comfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Lisanin.%20For%20her%20part%2C%20Wood%20loves%20down%20cushions.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20they%20make%20a%20more%20comfortable%20seat%20that%20can%20be%20fluffed%20and%20plumped%20to%20better%20fit%20different%20body%20types%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReturns%20and%20warranties%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPolicies%20vary%20by%20brand%2C%20but%20many%20companies%20offer%20a%20limited%20or%20lifetime%20warranty%20on%20the%20sofa's%20frame%20and%20hard%20components%20but%20not%20the%20upholstery.%20Return%20policies%20are%20also%20unique%20to%20each%20brand%2C%20but%20many%20offer%20a%20refund%20if%20the%20sofa%20is%20returned%20in%20good%20condition%2030%20days%20from%20the%20date%20of%20delivery%2C%20though%20restocking%20fees%20typically%20apply.%20However%2C%20some%20brands%2C%20like%20West%20Elm%20and%20Joybird%2C%20do%20not%20allow%20returns%20on%20custom-made%20pieces.%20Be%20sure%20to%20read%20each%20company's%20rules%20thoroughly%20before%20purchasing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228cfc9912-42b8-4dc9-97f0-9888ea053b07%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20tested%20sofas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20sections%20of%20the%20Sundays%20Movie%20Nights%20couch%20shown%20in%20the%20foreground%2C%20while%20a%20full%20Burrow%20Nomad%20Couch%20sits%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63876f3465ca3a0018ffc95a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20tested%20each%20sofa%20for%20months%20on%20end%20in%20our%20own%20homes%2C%20evaluating%20everything%20from%20ordering%20experience%20and%20delivery%20to%20long-term%20comfort.%20Here's%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20Sunday's%20Movie%20Night%20sofa%20next%20to%20the%20Burrow%20Nomad.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20test%20every%20sofa%20in%20our%20own%20homes%20and%20spend%20months%20%E2%80%94%20if%20not%20years%20%E2%80%94%20putting%20them%20through%20the%20paces.%20We%20lounge%20on%20them%2C%20work%20on%20them%2C%20sleep%20on%20them%2C%20play%20with%20kids%20and%20pets%20on%20them%2C%20and%20unintentionally%20spill%20food%20and%20drinks%20on%20them.%20While%20we're%20at%20it%2C%20we're%20thinking%20about%20the%20following%20criteria%20to%20determine%20which%20ones%20deserve%20to%20be%20named%20the%20best%20sofas%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237b68f7a-10a4-49eb-8646-326f081ee1dc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20we%20test%20is%20the%20comfort%20and%20firmness%20of%20the%20seat%20cushion.%20Is%20it%20so%20deep%20and%20soft%20that%20we%20have%20trouble%20getting%20up%20or%20so%20narrow%20and%20firm%20that%20we%20can't%20relax%3F%20We%20also%20consider%20how%20supportive%20the%20sofa%20back%20is%2C%20and%20if%20it%20causes%20slouching%2C%20straining%2C%20or%20feels%20so%20uncomfortable%20that%20we%20can't%20sit%20for%20long%20periods%20of%20time.%20Lastly%2C%20we%20look%20at%20the%20cushion's%20edges%2C%20and%20whether%20they%20are%20as%20firm%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20cushion%20or%20cause%20us%20to%20sink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2265a4b658-c5ce-44ba-b082-af7da1017752%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EConstruction%20and%20durability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20feel%20of%20the%20sofa%2C%20we%20inspect%20the%20quality%20of%20its%20construction.%20We%20check%20the%20sturdiness%20of%20its%20frame%2C%20whether%20it's%20made%20from%20solid%2C%20kiln-dried%20hardwood%20(our%20preference)%2C%20engineered%20wood%2C%20or%20another%20material.%20Upholstery%20is%20equally%20important.%20We%20test%20a%20variety%20of%20materials%2C%20including%20leather%2C%20velvet%2C%20performance%20weave%2C%20and%20linen%2C%20to%20verify%20their%20quality%20and%20claims.%20Do%20they%20pill%2C%20fade%2C%20or%20wear%20over%20time%3F%20How%20well%20do%20they%20resist%20stains%20and%20stand%20up%20to%20pet%20claws%3F%20And%20since%20sofas%20aren't%20cheap%2C%20we%20consider%20whether%20the%20cushions%20maintain%20their%20resiliency%20after%20repeated%20use%20or%20show%20signs%20of%20sagging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217d4441f-93c1-48b9-a74a-57321b3746d8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAssembly%20%26amp%3B%20delivery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tried%20threshold%20delivery%20and%20white-glove%20delivery%20to%20see%20what%20each%20experience%20was%20like%20and%20test%20the%20quality%20of%20service.%20Is%20it%20worth%20paying%20extra%20to%20have%20delivery%20people%20carry%20the%20sofa%20into%20our%20homes%20or%20did%20sofa%20pieces%20arrive%20in%20individual%20boxes%20that%20we%20could%20manage%20on%20our%20own%3F%20We%20then%20consider%20how%20much%20effort%20and%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20get%20the%20sofa%20in%20sitting%20condition%2C%20whether%20we%20assemble%20it%20ourselves%20or%20have%20the%20delivery%20people%20do%20it%20for%20us.%20And%2C%20of%20course%20we%20look%20carefully%20for%20any%20damage%20to%20the%20frame%20or%20fabric%20that%20might%20have%20occurred%20during%20shipping%20and%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cbe9f895-4a67-455d-a232-1be5921a4ceb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong-term%20testing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20test%20each%20sofa%20in%20our%20homes%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20six%20months%20to%20see%20how%20well%20it%20holds%20up.%20We%20want%20to%20see%20if%20the%20cushions%20have%20flattened%20or%20lost%20firmness%2C%20whether%20the%20couch%20is%20more%20or%20less%20comfortable%20now%20that%20it's%20lived%20in%2C%20how%20well%20the%20fabric%20held%20up%20to%20wear%20and%20stains%2C%20and%20if%20the%20frame%20has%20become%20wobbly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22addd3704-ebcc-4d83-a708-422071a0e7ae%5C%22%3EMeet%20the%20expert%20behind%20the%20guide%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMark%20Marino%2C%20contributor%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20have%20over%20two%20decades%20of%20experience%20in%20creating%20lifestyle%20content%2C%20including%20testing%20and%20reviewing%20the%20best%20home%20and%20kitchen%20products%20such%20as%20mattresses%2C%20pillows%2C%20bedding%2C%20sofas%2C%20vacuums%20and%20more.%20For%20this%20guide%2C%20I%20analyzed%20testing%20insights%20from%20BI%20staffers%20to%20curate%20this%20list%20of%20the%20best%20sofas%20we've%20tested%20in%20our%20own%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b51f1ca3-9600-41f8-8f65-db0c0fce5706%5C%22%3ESofa%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20long%20should%20a%20sofa%20last%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20lifespan%20of%20a%20sofa%20is%207%20to%2015%20years%20but%20could%20be%20less%20or%20more%20depending%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20its%20materials%20and%20how%20you%20care%20for%20it.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20be%20cautious%20with%20lower-quality%20frames%20like%20particleboard%20as%20well%20as%20delicate%20fabrics%20in%20high-traffic%20homes%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Lisanin.%20Stick%20to%20sofas%20crafted%20with%20a%20kiln-dried%20hardwood%20frame%20and%20durable%2C%20stain-resistant%20fabrics%20with%20a%20tight%20weave.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20you%20might%20pay%20a%20bit%20more%20upfront%2C%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20keep%20this%20sofa%20for%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Wood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20modular%20sofas%20worth%20it%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20modular%20sofas%20are%20worth%20it%20because%20they're%20designed%20to%20grow%20with%20you.%20The%20pieces%20can%20be%20added%20to%2C%20removed%2C%20and%20arranged%20to%20fit%20just%20about%20any%20space.%20Modular%20sofas%20are%20a%20great%20choice%20for%20apartments%2C%20and%20some%20are%20designed%20with%20space%20for%20storage%20and%20can%20convert%20into%20a%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat's%20the%20best%20sofa%20fabric%20for%20pets%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EPerformance%20fabrics%20are%20the%20best%20sofa%20fabric%20for%20pets%20because%20they're%20treated%20to%20resist%20stains.%20%26quot%3BYou%20still%20need%20to%20react%20when%20you%20see%20a%20stain%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Wood%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20a%20performance%20linen%20can%20easily%20be%20cleaned%20when%20muddy%20paws%20slip%20into%20the%20house%20and%20jump%20onto%20the%20sofa.%26quot%3B%20Fabrics%20that%20pull%20easily%2C%20like%20boucl%C3%A9%20and%20tweed%2C%20are%20not%20pet-friendly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20white%20glove%20delivery%20worth%20it%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20ordering%20a%20modular%20sofa%2C%20which%20typically%20ships%20to%20your%20doorstep%20in%20several%20boxes%2C%20you%20probably%20don't%20need%20to%20spend%20additional%20money%20to%20have%20someone%20carry%20the%20pieces%20inside%20and%20assemble%20them.%20However%2C%20most%20of%20our%20testers%20used%20white%20glove%20delivery%20for%20more%20fully%20assembled%20sofas%20and%20found%20that%20it%20was%20worth%20the%20additional%20fee%20to%20not%20have%20to%20lug%20the%20large%2C%20heavy%20furniture%20indoors%20and%20do%20any%20necessary%20assembly%20and%20cleanup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-sofa%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773344333000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b30273a96e437d6eb8393c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-sofa%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20tested%20the%20best%20couches%20for%20comfort%2C%20durability%2C%20and%20style%20in%20our%20homes.%20Our%20top%20sofas%20include%20custom%2C%20modular%2C%20sleeper%2C%20and%20sectional%20designs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mark%20Marino)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-sofa%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20Yuvraj%20Singh%20attend%20Gaurav%20Kapur%E2%80%93Kritika%20wedding%20reception%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773344137000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129523067%2Cimgsize-104184.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsachin-tendulkar-sunil-gavaskar-yuvraj-singh-naseeruddin-shah-and-others-attend-gaurav-kapurkritika-kamras-wedding-reception%2Farticleshow%2F129523067.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Newlyweds%20Gaurav%20Kapur%20and%20Kritika%20Kamra%20hosted%20a%20wedding%20reception%20on%20Thursday%20evening%2C%20bringing%20together%20close%20family%20members%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20personalities%20from%20the%20cricket%20and%20film%20industries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20ENTERTAINMENT%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Celebs%20attend%20Gaurav%20Kapur%E2%80%93Kritika%20Kamra%E2%80%99s%20wedding%20reception%22%2C%22content%22%3