3E%3Cp%3EPop%20stars%2C%20you%20can%20breathe%20easy.%20The%20debut%20single%20from%20AI-generated%20triple-threat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrands-torn-on-whether-to-embrace-ai-influencers-or-run-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETilly%20Norwood%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20evidence%20that%20your%20jobs%20are%20safe%20%E2%80%94%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20single's%204-minute%20music%20video%2C%20which%20first%20hit%20streaming%20services%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20is%20a%20montage%20of%20obviously%20AI-generated%20scenes%2C%20often%20intentionally%20over-the-top%2C%20depicting%20Norwood's%20imaginary%20path%20to%20global%20superstardom.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20she%20is%20hounded%20by%20paparazzi.%20At%20another%2C%20she%20performs%20for%20a%20sold-out%20stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20talk%20about%20me%2C%20they%20don't%20see%2FThe%20human%20spark%2C%20the%20creativity%2FBehind%20the%20code%2C%20behind%20the%20light%2FI'm%20just%20a%20tool%2C%20but%20I've%20got%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Norwood%20sings%20in%20%26quot%3BTake%20the%20Lead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FG7V2Biy3omw%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Tilly%20Norwood%20%7C%20Take%20The%20Lead%20(Official%20Music%20Video)%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reaction%20to%20the%20song%20and%20its%20video%2C%20which%20has%20over%20100%2C000%20views%20on%20YouTube%20as%20of%20Thursday%2C%20has%20been%20mixed%20at%20best.%20However%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Particle6%2C%20the%20AI%20studio%20behind%20Norwood's%20career%20(or%20whatever)%2C%20said%20releasing%20a%20chart-topping%20track%20was%20not%20the%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20made%20the%20video%20for%20'Take%20the%20Lead'%20with%20Tilly%20Norwood%2C%20the%20goal%20wasn't%20just%20to%20release%20a%20track%20or%20seek%20music%20chart%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20Particle6%20founder%20Eline%20van%20der%20Velden%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20to%20show%20people%20the%20current%20capabilities%20of%20AI%20and%20how%20actors%20and%20AI%20can%20now%20work%20together%20in%20a%20hybrid%20way%20with%20performance%20capture%2C%20and%20demonstrate%20that%20human%20input%20is%20still%20key.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20the%20music%20video%2C%20the%20company%20notes%20that%2018%20%26quot%3Breal%20humans%26quot%3B%20were%20behind%20the%20production%2C%20including%20prompters%2C%20production%20designers%2C%20editors%2C%20and%20an%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20divided%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-film-movie-ethics-conflict-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentertainment%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Supporters%20think%20the%20tech%20could%20shorten%20production%20time%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-ted-sarandos-james-camerson-ai-makes-movies-better-cheaper-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Critics%20worry%20AI%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-the-music-industry-is-changing-its-tune-on-ai-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etake%20human%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20infringe%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-ai-tools-copyright-infringement-big-tech-openai-anthropic-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecopyrighted%20material%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%2C%20as%20Matthew%20McConaughey%20has%20warned%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatthew-mcconaughey-trademark-likeness-ai-hollwood-actors-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5