er%20software%20as%20a%20service%2C%20or%20SaaS.%20I've%20covered%20this%20deeply%20for%20about%20a%20year%2C%20so%20this%20wasn't%20a%20surprise.%20But%20one%20of%20his%20main%20messages%20was%20unexpected%20%E2%80%94%20and%20is%20already%20proving%20prescient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20CEO%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-tech-companies-are-most-underwater-on-employee-stock-awards-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estock-based%20compensation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20SBC%2C%20is%20too%20high%20for%20SaaS%20companies%20now.%20Future%20revenue%20growth%20may%20not%20be%20as%20strong%20anymore%2C%20so%20SBC%20has%20to%20come%20down%2C%20and%20the%20financial%20discipline%20of%20the%20software%20industry%20has%20to%20improve.%20This%20year%2C%20SaaS%20companies%20will%20have%20to%20cut%20a%20lot%20of%20employees%20to%20adjust%2C%20he%20predicted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20explain%20this%20more%20in%20a%20second%2C%20but%20this%20reality%20is%20already%20beginning%20to%20play%20out.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20prominent%20software%20provider%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatlassian-layoff-global-workforce-attributes-it-to-the-ai-era-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAtlassian%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20it's%20cutting%2010%25%20of%20its%20workforce.%20That%20followed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-jack-dorsey-ai-impact-as-block-cuts-layoffs-workforce-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlock's%2040%25%20job%20cuts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20companies%20attributed%20some%20of%20these%20layoffs%20to%20the%20impact%20of%20generative%20AI.%20However%2C%20they%20both%20said%20they're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjack-dorsey-block-hiring-senior-ai-talent-iafter-layoffs-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estill%20hiring%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFive%20years%20from%20now%2C%20we'll%20have%20more%20engineers%20working%20for%20our%20company%20than%20we%20do%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Atlassian%20CEO%20Mike%20Cannon-Brooks%20said%20in%20October%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20will%20be%20more%20efficient.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what's%20really%20happening%20here%3F%20Let's%20go%20back%20to%20the%20weekend%20call%20I%20got%20from%20that%20other%20software%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227beb6f0f-919d-46d8-b562-cd2b022a2646%5C%22%3EThe%20rise%20of%20cheaper%20software%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20broad%20message%20he%20shared%20is%20that%20generative%20AI%20is%20making%20it%20much%20easier%20to%20create%20software.%20This%20means%20the%20supply%20of%20software%20is%20skyrocketing%2C%20so%20according%20to%20the%20law%20of%20supply%20and%20demand%2C%20the%20value%20of%20software%20is%20falling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaaspocalypse-ai-software-overreaction-premature-obituary-openai-anthropic-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewon't%20mean%20the%20death%20of%20SaaS%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20fact%2C%20cheaper%20and%20more%20prevalent%20software%20will%20be%20a%20huge%20boon%20to%20the%20tech%20industry%20because%20more%20people%20will%20use%20it.%20And%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-hiring-jobs-ai-supposedly-destroying-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esmart%20software%20engineers%20will%20be%20needed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20check%20that%20all%20this%20software%20is%20still%20working%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20understand%20deeply%20%3Cem%3Ewhy%3C%2Fem%3E%20it's%20working%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEngineering%20is%20changing%2C%20and%20great%20engineers%20are%20more%20important%20than%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Boris%20Cherny%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20Code%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20drivers%20of%20AI%20software%20disruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what's%20likely%20happening%20is%20that%20generative%20AI%20is%20changing%20how%20software%20is%20made%20and%20maintained%2C%20and%20upending%20how%20software%20companies%20charge%20for%20their%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20this%20could%20mean%20slower%20revenue%20growth%20for%20software%20providers.%20And%20this%20is%20what%20brings%20us%20back%20to%20the%20need%20for%20more%20financial%20discipline%20in%20the%20sector%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20stock-based%20compensation%2C%20or%20SBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngineers%20and%20other%20tech%20talent%20are%20wooed%20by%20software%20companies%20with%20generous%20chunks%20of%20equity%2C%20known%20as%20restricted%20stock%20units%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstock-options%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERSUs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20awards%20are%20often%20valued%20based%20on%20the%20market%20price%20on%20the%20day%20they're%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20works%20well%20when%20stocks%20are%20rising.%20But%20software%20stocks%20have%20taken%20a%20beating%20in%20recent%20months%20on%20concern%20about%20slowing%20growth%20and%20the%20potential%20impact%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20keep%20the%20same%20level%20of%20stock%20compensation%20with%20the%20same%20size%20workforce%2C%20software%20companies%20will%20soon%20have%20to%20issue%20millions%20of%20extra%20shares.%20That%20will%20dilute%20existing%20shareholders%20and%20cut%20deeply%20into%20future%20earnings%20per%20share%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20measures%20of%20any%20company's%20financial%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSBC%20(stock-based%20compensation)%20is%20coming%20up%20a%20lot%20more%20in%20our%20investor%20conversations%2C%26quot%3B%20Raimo%20Lenshow%2C%20a%20software%20analyst%20at%20Barclays%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20research%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20assessed%20software%20company%20valuations%20after%20the%20recent%20SaaS%20swoon%20in%20the%20market.%20Stocks%20looked%20more%20compelling%2C%20until%20he%20included%20SBC%20in%20the%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdjusting%20for%20the%20large%20levels%20of%20stock-based%20compensation%2C%20the%20situation%20looks%20less%20rosy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20can%20software%20companies%20do%20to%20address%20investor%20concerns%20about%20this%3F%20One%20solution%20is%20to%20cut%20jobs.%20That%20immediately%20reduces%20stock-based%20compensation%20costs%2C%20because%20companies%20don't%20need%20to%20issue%20more%20new%20stock%20to%20those%20folks%20being%20let%20go%20(and%20future%20vesting%20ends%20for%20these%20people%2C%20too).%20This%20improves%20earnings%2C%20based%20on%20old-school%20GAAP%20measures%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20where%20investors%20like%20to%20go%20during%20times%20of%20stress%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20big%20driver%20of%20Atlassian's%20job%20cuts%20this%20week%2C%20according%20to%20William%20Blair%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Atlassian%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20moderate%20SBC%20lower%20as%20it%20has%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20stock%20comp%20in%20the%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote%20in%20a%20research%20note.%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20recently%20become%20a%20louder%20conversation%20as%20tech%20investors%20look%20for%20more%20profits%20from%20scaled%20businesses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20happened%20in%202022%20as%20well%2C%20and%20Business%20Insider%20covered%20it%20a%20lot.%20Back%20then%2C%20the%20tech%20industry%20was%20coming%20down%20hard%20from%20a%20pandemic-era%20hiring%20binge.%20Growth%20was%20slowing%20and%20SBC%20looked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchart-shows-most-unsustainable-tech-company-compensation-plans-rsus-equity-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompletely%20unsustainable%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Brutal%20financial%20discipline%20ensued%20and%20thousands%20of%20tech%20workers%20lost%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20in%20a%20similar%20moment%20now%2C%20according%20to%20that%20CEO%20who%20called%20me%20on%20the%20weekend.%20Before%20he%20got%20off%20the%20phone%2C%20he%20said%20financial%20discipline%20has%20to%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-ceo-stock-based-compensation-layoffs-ai-saas-atlassian-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773338565000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2fa30a7a4f9df67ba3ea9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-ceo-stock-based-compensation-layoffs-ai-saas-atlassian-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Generative%20AI%20is%20reshaping%20SaaS%2C%20leading%20Atlassian%20and%20Block%20to%20cut%20jobs.%20Stock-based%20compensation%20and%20financial%20discipline%20are%20key%20issues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abarr%40businessinsider.com%20(Alistair%20Barr)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-ceo-stock-based-compensation-layoffs-ai-saas-atlassian-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Madhya%20Pradesh%20To%20Tag%2040%20Lakh%20Stray%20Cattle%20With%20Saffron%20Tags%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22In%20a%20major%20step%20aimed%20at%20tackling%20the%20growing%20menace%20of%20stray%20cattle%20on%20roads%20and%20farms%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20proposal%20to%20tag%2