mpany%20is%20courting%20Gen%20Z.%3Cp%3ETinder%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETinder%20announced%20a%20slew%20of%20new%20products%20for%202026%2C%20including%20an%20astrology%20mode%2C%20AI%20photo%20enhancements%2C%20and%20IRL%20events.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatch-group-spencer-rascoff-employee-letter-online-app-critique-numbers-2025-3%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpencer%20Rascoff%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Tinder%20couldn't%20%26quot%3Bput%20our%20heads%20in%20the%20sand%20and%20stay%20wedded%20to%20past%20practice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERascoff%20hopes%20the%20Events%20feature%20will%20bring%20in%20users%20who%20have%20soured%20on%20dating%20apps.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETinder%20wants%20you%20to%20get%20offline.%20No%2C%20really.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftinder-cultural-reset-gen-z-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworld's%20biggest%20dating%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20a%20variety%20of%20new%20features%20for%202026%20at%20its%20product%20conference%2C%20Tinder%20Sparks.%20There%20will%20be%20ways%20to%20match%20based%20on%20music%20taste%20and%20astrology%2C%20to%20enhance%20photos%20with%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20skip%20out%20on%20the%20back-and-forth%20of%20online%20dating%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20%26quot%3BEvents%26quot%3B%20tab%2C%20which%20is%20testing%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20this%20month%2C%20will%20connect%20users%20to%20in-person%20dating%20events.%20In%20an%20exclusive%20interview%2C%20CEO%20Spencer%20Rascoff%20said%20that%20IRL%20dating%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20solution%26quot%3B%20for%20Gen%20Z%20daters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvents%20are%20fun%2C%20they're%20low-pressure%2C%20they're%20social%2C%20they're%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20Rascoff%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20bringing%20Tinder%20into%20the%20physical%20world%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20consistent%20with%20our%20users'%20lifestyles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Events%20tab%20is%20placed%20squarely%20next%20to%20the%20swiping%20tab%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sign%2C%20Rascoff%20said%2C%20of%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20the%20company.%20Users%20can%20browse%20listings%20with%20attendee%20counts%20and%20blurred%20photos.%20Once%20the%20user%20registers%2C%20the%20photos%20will%20unblur%2C%20and%20they%20can%20see%20some%20of%20the%20faces%20that%20will%20be%20in%20attendance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20fairly%20notable%20about-face%20for%20a%20company%20that%20once%20centered%20around%20the%20endless%20possibilities%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftinder-swipe-right-inventor-how-he-came-up-with-it-2016-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESwipe%20Right%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20Indeed%2C%20many%20users%20have%20been%20tiring%20of%20the%20apps%20entirely%3B%20you%20may%20have%20heard%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-dating-app-ai-swipe-fatigue-assistant-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eswipe%20fatigue%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20run%20a%20consumer%20internet%20company%2C%20you%20have%20to%20stay%20attentive%20to%20changing%20consumer%20tastes%2C%26quot%3B%20Rascoff%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20put%20our%20heads%20in%20the%20sand%20and%20stay%20wedded%20to%20past%20practice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225216%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tinder's%20Events%20tab%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2e094a96e437d6eb83597%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETinder%20is%20testing%20an%20in-person%20dating%20feature%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3Cp%3ETinder%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERascoff%20hopes%20that%20events%20will%20help%20bring%20in%20those%20worried%20by%20or%20frustrated%20with%20online%20dating.%20He%20compared%20it%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-rentals-experiences-services-patrick-mahomes-how-explained-cost-2025-05%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirbnb's%20experiences%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20company%20uses%20luxury%20houses%20and%20villas%20to%20get%20people%20to%20reconsider%20%26quot%3Balternative%20accommodations%26quot%3B%20and%2C%20hopefully%2C%20return%20to%20their%20core%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Rascoff's%20takeover%20in%202025%2C%20he's%20attempted%20to%20steer%20the%20app%20clear%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fwhat-is-tinder%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehookup%20reputation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20IRL%20events%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20drive%20reconsideration%20of%20Tinder%20from%20people%20who%20have%20formed%20an%20opinion%2C%26quot%3B%20Rascoff%20said.%20He%20described%20an%20anti-Tinder%20user%20who%20downloads%20for%20the%20events%2C%20and%20eventually%20uses%20it%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Balibi%26quot%3B%20to%20start%20swiping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20upcoming%20features%20include%20specialty%20swiping%20modes%20for%20music%20and%20astrology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERascoff%20shared%20stories%20of%20two%20recent%20job%20interviews%20he%20held%20with%20Gen%20Z%20candidates.%20One%20responded%20to%20a%20question%20about%20why%20they%20were%20leaving%20their%20current%20company%20with%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20Gemini.%26quot%3B%20Another%20responded%20to%20why%20they%20went%20into%20this%20field%20with%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20I'm%20a%20Taurus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225520%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tinder's%20Astrology%20Mode%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2e041a7a4f9df67ba3bb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETi