%20city%20long%20defined%20by%20its%20reputation%20as%20a%20safe%20haven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20authorities%20said%20a%20drone%20hit%20a%20building%20in%20Dubai%20Creek%20Harbour%2C%20and%20debris%20from%20an%20intercepted%20attack%20struck%20the%20facade%20of%20a%20building%20on%20Sheikh%20Zayed%20Road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20confirmation%20from%20authorities%20came%20after%20residents%20received%20missile%20alerts%20overnight%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20several%20such%20alerts%20issued%20since%20the%20war%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20days%20after%20the%20first%20strikes%20over%20the%20weekend%20that%20the%20war%20broke%20out%2C%20and%20as%20travel%20chaos%20ensued%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdubai-expat-dream-safe-haven-tax-middle-east-turmoil-iran-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseveral%20expats%20told%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20felt%20safe%20and%20protected%20in%20Dubai%2C%20and%20that%20people%20watching%20from%20afar%20were%20%26quot%3Brelishing%26quot%3B%20the%20notion%20that%20Dubai%20might%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20for%20the%20city%20whose%20reputation%20is%20predicated%20on%20its%20safe%20haven%20status%2C%20what%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20days%20since%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222343%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20steeplejack%20assesses%20visible%20damage%2C%20including%20blown-out%20windows%2C%20on%20the%20facade%20of%20a%20building.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2c6f9a96e437d6eb83111%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221562%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20damage%20to%20the%20facade%20of%20a%20building%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20Dubai's%20Creek%20Harbour.%3Cp%3EAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ca289a10-70d1-490f-959e-6f21f2b59ddd%5C%22%3EGuidance%20to%20schools%20and%20companies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%20moved%20schools%20and%2