ng%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-government-partial-shutdown-minnesota-homeland-security-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epartial%20government%20shutdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20like%20playing%20a%20game%20of%20TSA%20line%20roulette.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20shortage%20of%20security%20agents%20at%20Houston's%20Hobby%20Airport%20and%20New%20Orleans'%20Louis%20Armstrong%20International%20Airport%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairport-delays-tsa-lines-partial-government-shutdown-list-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eled%20to%20extraordinary%20security%20queues%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20stretched%20up%20to%20three%20hours%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20general%20line%20in%20Houston%20snaked%20into%20the%20parking%20garage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirports%20in%20San%20Juan%2C%20Atlanta%2C%20and%20Charlotte%20have%20similarly%20told%20travelers%20to%20budget%20extra%20time%20for%20staffing-related%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-check-tsa-wait-times-before-your-flight-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esecurity%20delays%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20many%20TSA%20agents%20%E2%80%94%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bessential%26quot%3B%20and%20required%20to%20work%20without%20pay%20during%20the%20shutdown%20%E2%80%94%20didn't%20show%20up.%20Wait%20times%20at%20these%20airports%20were%20under%2030%20minutes%20on%20Thursday%2C%20but%20that%20could%20change%20with%20little%20notice%20as%20the%20busy%20spring%20break%20season%20goes%20into%20full%20swing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgents%20are%20expected%20to%20receive%20their%20first%20%240%20paycheck%20this%20weekend%2C%20raising%20the%20likelihood%20that%20more%20fed-up%20agents%20will%20call%20in%20sick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Harteveldt%2C%20a%20travel%20analyst%20and%20the%20president%20of%20Atmosphere%20Research%20Group%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%2C%20for%20now%2C%20the%20TSA%20chaos%20appears%20localized%20to%20select%20airports%20where%20mass%20callouts%20collided%20with%20peak%20spring%20break%20travel.%20The%20US%20Travel%20Association%20estimated%20that%20a%20record%20171%20million%20people%20will%20fly%20in%20March%20and%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-mess-at-several-us-airports-long-lines-others-fine-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eairports%20across%20the%20US%20are%20operating%20normally%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Houston's%20larger%20airport%2C%20George%20Bush%20Intercontinental%2C%20reported%20wait%20times%20as%20short%20as%20a%20few%20minutes%20Thursday%20morning%3B%20major%20hubs%20like%20New%20York%2C%20Boston%2C%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20Miami%2C%20and%20Dallas-Fort%20Worth%20were%20reporting%2020%20minutes%20or%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20this%20hasn't%20made%20the%20situation%20any%20less%20confusing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarteveldt%20said%20it's%20likely%20the%20chaos%20will%20spread%20to%20other%20airports%20the%20longer%20security%20officers%20work%20without%20pay%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20coming%20missed%20paycheck%20likely%20motivating%20even%20more%20callouts%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-traffic-control-shortages-airport-flight-delays-government-shutdown-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eas%20seen%20during%20the%20full%20government%20shutdown%20in%20October%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20early%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20from%20the%20last%20government%20shutdown%20that%20it's%20difficult%20for%20TSA%20employees%20to%20work%20for%20a%20sustained%20period%20without%20any%20income%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20these%20individuals%20calling%20out%20or%20leaving%20to%20work%20a%20supplementary%20job%20that%20will%20provide%20some%20type%20of%20pay%20is%20completely%20understandable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20tips%20if%20you're%20headed%20to%20the%20airport%20as%20the%20shutdown%20drags%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0cfd8e2-1574-43f3-898b-fedf321fe784%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBudget%20extra%20time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20the%20partial%20shutdown%20and%20higher%20fuel%20prices%20due%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Iran%2C%20Harteveldt%20advised%20that%20travelers%20who%20haven't%20yet%20booked%20should%20consider%20postponing%20until%20things%20are%20%26quot%3Bcalmer%20and%20more%20predictable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsider%20taking%20a%20train%20or%20driving%20if%20you%20must%20travel.%20If%20you%20must%20fly%2C%20be%20sure%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-wait-times-government-shutdown-airports-photos-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebudget%20extra%20time%20for%20security%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whether%20the%20airport%20is%20bottlenecked%20or%20running%20normally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226940%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Passengers%20in%20TSA%20line%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69adf7f0d3e2f1aef36a339e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224627%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20TSA%20agent%20shortage%20caused%20by%20the%20partial%20government%20shutdown%20has%20led%20to%20long%20lines%20at%20airport%20security.%3Cp%3ERONALDO%20SCHEMIDT%20%2F%20AFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShort-staffed%20airports%20may%20be%20less%20diligent%20in%20updating%20security%20wait%20times%2C%20so%20the%2015-%20or%2030-minute%20waits%20you%20see%20online%20may%20not%20be%20accurate%2C%26quot%3B%20Harteveldt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHouston%20Hobby%20Airport%20on%20Tuesday%20told%20passengers%20to%20arrive%20three%20hours%20early%20for%20domestic%20flights%20and%20four%20hours%20early%20for%20international%20flights%20due%20to%20staffing%20shortages%20at%20TSA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESally%20French%2C%20a%20travel%20analyst%20at%20NerdWallet%2C%20said%20she%20usually%20recommends%20travelers%20use%20the%20MyTSA%20mobile%20app%20to%20check%20security%20lines%20ahead%20of%20time%2C%20but%20warned%20it%20may%20not%20be%20accurate%20because%20it%20is%20not%20being%20updated%20during%20the%20shutdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2205957dfc-c2c0-496b-b87b-b6803d0eb1e5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20in%20the%20fast%20lane%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETravelers%20should%20check%20whether%20their%20ticket%20and%20the%20airport%20allow%20them%20to%20use%20security%20lanes%20that%20bypass%20the%20general%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20opt%20into%20the%20TSA's%20Touchless%20ID%2C%20that%20may%20be%20faster%2C%20but%20it%20and%20other%20expedited%20lines%20still%20may%20be%20closed%20during%20the%20shutdown%2C%26quot%3B%20Harteveldt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22TSA%20agent%20at%20Touchless%20ID%20stand%20in%20Charlotte.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b06c4f441e48aec3a1d63a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETouchless%20ID%20still%20requires%20an%20agent%20present%20to%20manage%20and%20monitor%20the%20station%2C%20but%20the%20ID%20process%20is%20faster.%3Cp%3ECharlotte%20Douglas%20International%20Airport%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fno-id-or-boarding-pass-for-security-at-more-airports-with-tsa-precheck-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETouchless%20ID%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20voluntary%20system%20that%20allows%20enrolled%20passengers%20to%20enter%20security%20using%20facial%20recognition%20instead%20of%20showing%20an%20ID%20and%20boarding%20pass%20to%20a%20TSA%20agent.%20Eligible%20travelers%20must%20have%20a%20passport%2C%20an%20active%20airline%20profile%2C%20and%20be%20a%20TSA%20PreCheck%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20feature%20is%20only%20available%20to%20passengers%20of%20participating%20airlines%20at%20certain%20major%20airports%20and%20may%20be%20unavailable%20during%20the%20shutdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrench%20said%20people%20with%20certain%20airline%20status%20or%20who%20bought%20higher-fare%20tickets%20should%20check%20if%20they%20have%20access%20to%20expedited%20security%20lanes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20airlines%20allow%20people%20to%20buy%20separate%20access%20to%20speedier%20lines%3A%20United's%20%26quot%3BPremiere%20Access%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20example%2C%20starts%20at%20%2424%20and%20includes%20an%20exclusive%20security%20line%2C%20though%20the%20perk%20is%20subject%20to%20availability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220ac2d53a-b186-4d96-afd4-8794e479b060%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInvest%20in%20TSA%20PreCheck%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrench%20said%20TSA%20PreCheck%20is%20among%20the%20most%20reliable%20ways%20to%20get%20through%20security%20faster%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20always%20recommend%20applying%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-precheck-etiquette-get-through-airport-security-fast%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETSA%20PreCheck%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20so%20many%20credit%20cards%20offer%20it%20as%20a%20benefit%20in%20that%20they%20cover%20your%20application%20fee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETSA%20PreCheck%20%E2%80%94%20which%20allows%20passengers%20to%20keep%20their%20toiletries%20and%20laptops%20in%20their%20bags%2C%20wear%20their%20shoes%20and%20jackets%2C%20and%20use%20a%20metal%20detector%20instead%20of%20full-body%20scanners%20%E2%80%94%20costs%20about%20%2476%20for%20a%20five-year%20membership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20TSA%20Precheck%20sign%20at%20William%20P.%20Hobby%20Airport%20in%20Houston.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aef2e2d3e2f1aef36a3b67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHOUSTON%2C%20TEXAS%20-%20MARCH%208%3A%20Airline%20passengers%20wait%20in%20long%20lines%20to%20get%20through%20the%20TSA%20security%20screening%20at%20William%20P.%20Hobby%20Airport%20in%20Houston%2C%20Sunday%2C%20March%208%2C%202026.%20The%20line%20stretched%20from%20the%20security%20checkpoint%20into%20the%20lower%20level%20baggage%20claim%20area%20to%20the%20lower%20level%20parking%20garage.%3Cp%3EBrett%20Coomer%2FHouston%20Chronicle%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20requires%20proof%20of%20US%20citizenship%20or%20residency%2C%20passing%20a%20background%20check%2C%20and%20completing%20an%20in-person%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECredit%20cards%20like%20the%20Chase%20Sapphire%20Reserve%20and%20the%20Capital%20One%20Venture%20offer%20PreCheck%20reimbursement.%20The%20quicker%20line%20typically%20requires%20fewer%20agents%20thanks%20to%20the%20less%20intensive%20screening%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-precheck-global-entry-lanes-suspended-airports-travel-time-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estill%20open%20at%20most%20airports%20despite%20DHS%20briefly%20closing%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20earlier%20in%20the%20shutdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclear-airport-security-tsa-id-checks-pre-check-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECLEAR%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20privately%20owned%20security%20program%20available%20at%20most%20major%20airports%2C%20is%20another%20option.%20Enrolled%20travelers%20verify%20their%20identity%20using%20biometrics%20and%20are%20then%20escorted%20to%20the%20front%20of%20the%20line%20%E2%80%94%20similar%20to%20Touchless%20ID.%20It's%20%24209%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a623cb47-f71a-4142-803b-f13349c098f0%5C%22%3EDon't%20bet%20on%20compensation%20from%20your%20airline%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20long%20TSA%20lines%20make%20you%20miss%20your%20flight%2C%20airlines%20will%20often%20rebook%20you%20on%20the%20next%20available%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20largely%20as%20much%20as%20airlines%20offer%20%E2%80%94%20the%20shutdown%20is%20out%20of%20their%20control%2C%20so%20any%20hotel%20or%20meal%20vouchers%20would%20be%20a%