6eb83198%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22715%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20moves%20in%20areas%20like%20defense%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20aerospace%20may%20already%20be%20priced%20in%2C%20B.%20Riley's%20Hogan%20said.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Christopher%20Bohn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20investors%20may%20feel%20the%20instinct%20to%20rush%20into%20areas%20of%20the%20market%20that%20could%20see%20a%20boost%20from%20the%20war%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-stock-picks-energy-market-oil-utilities-sector-outperforms-buy-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eenergy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20aerospace%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-defense-stocks-military-aerospace-lmt-hii-baesy-rnmby-bwxt-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edefense%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20problem%20with%20that%20strategy%20is%20that%20by%20the%20time%20most%20investors%20have%20caught%20on%2C%20the%20gains%20in%20those%20sectors%20have%20largely%20been%20priced%20in%2C%20meaning%20many%20traders%20risk%20losing%20money%2C%20Hogan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20how%20many%20investors%20piled%20into%20defense%20stocks%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year%20when%20the%20US%20raided%20Venezuela%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fishares-us-aerospace-defense-etf-us4642887602%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EiShares%20US%20Aerospace%20%26amp%3B%20Defense%20ETF%3C%2Fa%3E%20rising%20as%20much%20as%209%25%20in%20the%20first%20two%20weeks%20of%20the%20year.%20The%20ETF%2C%20though%2C%20is%20now%20down%203%25%20from%20its%20mid-January%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPiling%20into%20some%20obvious%20winners%20likely%20can%20cost%20you%20money%20as%20well%2C%20so%20I%20wouldn't%20chase%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a762b7b8-0cd3-483f-8100-1d8fd762da2f%5C%22%3E2.%20Don't%20load%20up%20on%20defensive%20investments%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20defensive%20areas%20of%20the%20market%2C%20such%20as%20industrials%2C%20consumer%20staples%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-cap-stocks-sp500-comparison-reasons-for-outperformance-rate-cuts-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esmall-cap%20stocks%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20outperforming%20recently.%20While%20investors%20have%20typically%20sought%20out%20these%20areas%20for%20safety%2C%20they%20look%20expensive%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20Hogan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20looking%20at%20making%20an%20investment%20at%20or%20near%20all-time%20highs%20in%20both%20sectors%2C%20which%20will%20likely%20see%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20reversion%20to%20the%20mean%20or%20a%20pullback%20once%20things%20get%20rectified%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAreas%20like%20small-caps%20have%20also%20been%20the%20most%20affected%20by%20the%20US-Iran%20turmoil%2C%20as%20higher%20inflation%20is%20likely%20to%20hit%20smaller%20companies%20the%20most%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeter%20Berezin%2C%20the%20chief%20global%20strategist%20at%20BCA%20Research%2C%20advised%20investors%20to%20be%20wary%20of%20areas%20of%20the%20market%20that%20could%20be%20impacted%20by%20inflation%2C%20such%20as%20bonds.%20While%20bonds%20are%20typically%20thought%20of%20as%20safe-havens%2C%20inflation%20can%20raise%20interest%20rates%20in%20the%20economy%20over%20the%20long%20run%2C%20which%20lifts%20bond%20yields%20and%20lowers%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20a%20stagflationary%20shock%2C%20so%20jumping%20into%20bonds%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20risky.%20Being%20in%20stocks%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20risky%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223a075ced-a124-44a7-b612-332e0320a996%5C%22%3E3.%20Consider%20beaten-down%20tech%20stocks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22software%20stock%20selloff%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2cc124d65ec517529e39e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJeenah%20Moon%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-stock-picks-to-buy-tech-dan-ives-iran-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETech%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20one%20area%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20that%20seems%20relatively%20immune%20to%20a%20potential%20oil-price%20shock%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20higher%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20going%20to%20stop%20using%20our%20iPhones%2C%26quot%3B%20B.%20Riley's%20Hogan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20last%20thing%20that%20we%20give%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sector%20is%20also%20trading%20at%20a%20discount%20after%20fears%20of%20an%20AI%20apocalypse%20ripped%20through%20software%20and%20other%20corners%20of%20the%20sector%20earlier%20in%202026.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20underexposed%20to%20technology%2C%20now%20might%20be%20the%20time%20to%20rotate%20into%20that%20and%20perhaps%20out%20of%20some%20of%20the%20sectors%20that%20have%20done%20very%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a10acfa7-c891-4331-a5f8-4aae3f7744ec%5C%22%3E4.%20Consider%20holding%20more%20cash%20on%20the%20sidelines%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20short-term%20investors%20who%20insist%20on%20making%20changes%20to%20their%20portfolio%2C%20a%20good%20option%20is%20to%20keep%20extra%20cash%20on%20the%20sidelines%20rather%20than%20taking%20on%20more%20risk%20in%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20market%2C%20according%20to%20BCA's%20Berezin.%20He%20pointed%20to%20the%20potential%20for%20higher%20inflation%20and%20stagflation%2C%20a%20dreaded%20scenario%20in%20which%20inflation%20rises%20while%20growth%20slows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20wasn't%20an%20economy%20that%20was%20firing%20all%20cylinders%20even%20before%20the%20oil%20shock%2C%20and%20if%20the%20oil%20shock%20persists%2C%20that%20could%20be%20enough%20to%20drag%20it%20down%20into%20a%20recession%20later%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Berezin%20said%2C%20advising%20investors%20to%20increase%20their%20allocation%20to%20cash%20instruments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Brown%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20strategist%20at%20Pepperstone%2C%20also%20advised%20short-term%20traders%20to%20have%20more%20cash%20on%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTake%20down%20exposure%20to%20global%20equities%2C%20given%20how%20uncertain%20and%20volatile%20the%20environment%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5b4d955-3a3e-4791-bb9d-baa2ac98dfe7%5C%22%3E5.%20Be%20wary%20of%20volatility-linked%20ETFs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blurred%20photo%20of%20a%20trader%20walking%20at%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2cc55a7a4f9df67ba3801%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBRYAN%20R.%20SMITH%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVolatility-linked%20ETFs%2C%20which%20gain%20the%20more%20volatile%20markets%20are%2C%20have%20been%20a%20hot%20investment%20in%20recent%20weeks.%20In%20particular%2C%20retail%20investors%20scooped%20up%20the%202x%20Long%20VIX%20Futures%20ETF%2C%20a%20fund%20that%20tracks%20the%20market's%20volatility%20gauge%2C%20and%20the%20ProShares%20UltraPro%20Short%20QQQ%20an%20inverse%20investment%20product%20that%20gains%20when%20the%20Nasdaq%20100%20declines%2C%20Vanda%20data%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20strategy%20is%20one%20way%20to%20hedge%20risk%20in%20markets%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20extremely%20risky%20in%20itself%2C%20Berezin%20said%2C%20as%20volatility%20can%20drop%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20VIX%20Index%2C%20the%20market's%20volatility%20gauge%2C%20is%20hovering%20around%2026%2C%20down%20from%20its%20peak%20of%2029%20earlier%20this%20month.%20Hogan%20said%20it%20is%20possible%20volatility%20has%20already%20peaked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20volatility%20ETF%20is%20by%20its%20nature%20extremely%20volatile%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20investors%20adding%20the%20instrument%20to%20their%20portfolios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20probably%20not%20one%20that%20the%20average%20retail%20investor%20should%20be%20looking%20at%2C%26quot%3B%20Pepperstone's%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-invest-stock-market-strategy-oil-us-iran-war-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773332403000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2e2bda96e437d6eb835f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-invest-stock-market-strategy-oil-us-iran-war-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Don't%20panic-sell%20or%20make%20drastic%20portfolio%20changes%2C%20market%20pros%20say.%20Here's%20what%20they%20say%20to%20do%20instead%20as%20the%20Iran%20war%20continues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40businessinsider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-invest-stock-market-strategy-oil-us-iran-war-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Honda%20takes%20a%20%2415.7%20billion%20hit%20as%20EV%20retreat%20continues%20to%20batter%20legacy%20automakers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Honda%200%20Saloon%20is%20parked%20on%20a%20showroom%20floor%20in%20front%20of%20a%20pink%20and%20purple%20digital%20screen.%20Several%20onlookers%20are%20surrounding%20the%20car%20and%20taking%20pictures.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2bdab4d65ec517529e258%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHonda%20is%20writing%20down%20%2415.7%20billion%20on%20its%20EV%20division.%3Cp%3EArtur%20Widak%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHonda%20said%20it%20booked%20a%20charge%20of%20up%20to%20%2415.7%20billion%20as%20it%20retreats%20from%20some%20EV%20plans.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Japanese%20automaker%20joins%20other%20global%20legacy%20automakers%20announcing%20billion-dollar%20EV%20charges.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Honda%200%20Saloon%2C%20Honda%200%20SUV%2C%20and%20Acura%20RSX%20EV%20are%20all%20canceled.%20It%20leaves%20Honda%20with%20one%20EV.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhonda-return-to-office-order-rto-us-staff-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHonda%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20taking%20a%20massive%20financial%20hit%20as%20it%20pulls%20back%20on%20its%20electric-vehicle%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Japanese%20automaker%20said%20it%20expects%20to%20write%20off%20up%20to%202.5%20trillion%20yen%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20%2415.7%20billion%20%E2%80%94%20as%20it%20reshapes%20its%20North%20American%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhonda-hybrids-ev-electric-vehicles-pivot-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEV%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Honda%20expects%20the%20charge%20will%20push%20profits%20into%20the%20red%20in%202026%2C%20marking%20its%20first%20annual%20loss%20in%20nearly%207%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20growing%20list%20of%20legacy%20automakers%20to%20announce%20multibillion-dollar%20hits%20as%20the%20industry%20recalibrates%20its%20electric%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EV%20pullback%20has%20gained%20momentum%20after%20the%20federal%20government%20ended%20the%20%247%2C500%20tax%20credit%20for%20US-built%20EVs%20under%20the%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%20in%20September.%20The%20rebate%20was%20intended%20to%20spur%20both%20EV%20adoption%20and%20US%20auto%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20automakers%20were%20investing%20in%20their%20EV%20platforms%20to%20align%20with%20the%20subsidies%2C%26quot%3B%20Seth%20Goldstein%2C%20an%20EV%20analyst%20at%20Morningstar%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20these%20expired%20early%20last%20September%2C%20this%20led%20automakers%20to%20adjust%20their%20investments%20and%20EV%20strategies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeep%20maker%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstellantis-stock-jeep-ram-chrysler-ev-retreat-26-billion-charge-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStellantis%20booked%20a%20%2426%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20charge%20after%20discontinuing%20several%20EVs%20and%20plug-in%20hybrids.%20Ford%20reported%20a%20%2419.5%20billion%20hit%20in%20December%20and%20canceled%20its%20F-150%20Lightning.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeneral-motors-ev-electric-vehicle-billions-loss-writedown-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Motors%20took%20a%20%246%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20charge%20as%20it%20slowed%20production%20across%20its%2011%20EV%20models.%20Volkswagen%20also%20had%20a%20%245.7%20billion%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20the%20five%20automaking%20behemoths%20have%20announced%20%2472.9%20billion%20in%20write-downs%20tied%20to%20EV%20portfolio%20adjustments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20yellow%20Acura%20RSX%20EV%20with%20a%20black%20roof%20and%20black%20wheels%20sits%20on%20a%20well-manicured%20lawn.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2ccf1a7a4f9df67ba3814%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHonda%20also%20said%20it%20would%20cancel%20US%20production%20of%20three%20cars%2C%20including%20the%20Acura%20RSX%20EV%2C%20shown%20above.%3Cp%3EAcura%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHonda%20said%20its%20EV%20reset%20stems%20from%20two%20main%20