2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20enjoyed%20nearly%20everything%20about%20this%20meal%2C%20which%20was%20packed%20with%20contrasting%20flavors%20and%20textures.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Mayor%20of%20Flavortown%2C%20Guy%20Fieri%20has%20plenty%20of%20ways%20to%20turn%20your%20average%20sandwich%20into%20a%20lunchtime%20staple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20previous%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Fieri%20shared%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguy-fieri-best-cooking-tips-for-beginners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etop%20tips%20for%20home%20cooks%3C%2Fa%3E%20looking%20to%20make%20restaurant-quality%20sandwiches%20in%20their%20own%20kitchens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20celebrity%20chef%20said%20a%20good%20sandwich%20starts%20with%20a%20solid%20foundation%20of%20sturdy%2C%20flavorful%20bread%20and%20combines%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20textures%20and%20flavors%20to%20keep%20the%20taste%20buds%20hungry%20for%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInspired%20to%20upgrade%20my%20own%20basic%20lunches%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20put%20his%20sandwich%20tips%20to%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227495250a-86dc-4d17-907a-2f49aaf7af10%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20Fieri's%20tips%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20headed%20to%20the%20grocery%20store%20for%20very%20specific%20ingredients%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22guy%20fieri%20sandwich%20ingredients%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6081a4614becb800190f68df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrom%20choosing%20the%20ingredients%20to%20building%20the%20meal%2C%20I%20tested%20out%20the%20celebrity%20chef's%20advice.%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%20for%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFieri%20mentioned%20using%20rolls%20or%20breads%20with%20a%20slightly%20sweet%20flavor%20to%20balance%20savory%20fillings%2C%20so%20I%20chose%20a%20simple%20potato%20bread.I%20also%20followed%20his%20advice%20when%20choosing%20the%20other%20ingredients%20for%20my%20sandwich%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20the%20acid%20of%20giardiniera.%20I%20love%20the%20crunch%20of%20giardiniera%2C%26quot%3B%20Fieri%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20really%20crispy%20lettuce.%20I%20like%20heirloom%20tomatoes%2C%20thinly%20sliced.%20I%20like%20sweet%20onions.%20I%20enjoy%20really%20good%20mustard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrying-guy-fieri-favorite-breakfast-dish-grits-recipe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echef's%20recommendation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20grabbed%20a%20jar%20of%20giardiniera%20%E2%80%94%20a%20pickled%20assortment%20of%20jalape%C3%B1os%2C%20cauliflower%2C%20and%20carrots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20found%20a%20picture-perfect%20heirloom%20tomato%2C%20fresh%20butter%20lettuce%2C%20and%20a%20red%20onion%20that%20I%20planned%20to%20quick%20pickle.%20For%20the%20protein%2C%20I%20opted%20for%20basic%20plant-based%20%26quot%3Bturkey%26quot%3B%20slices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20already%20had%20some%20brown%20mustard%20and%20cheese%20at%20home%2C%20but%20I%20also%20picked%20up%20the%20ingredients%20for%20Fieri's%20famous%20donkey%20sauce%2C%20including%20roasted%20garlic%2C%20mayonnaise%2C%20yellow%20mustard%2C%20salt%2C%20pepper%2C%20and%20Worcestershire%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220068db2a-36aa-4c84-8e09-87b41c1869ff%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBefore%20anything%20else%2C%20I%20roasted%20the%20garlic%20for%20the%20donkey%20sauce%20and%20pickled%20the%20red%20onion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Fieri's%20advice%20to%20add%20giardiniera%20to%20my%20dish%2C%20I%20was%20skeptical%20because%20I'm%20not%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20carrots%20or%20cauliflower.%20However%2C%20I%20do%20love%20pickled%20onions%2C%20so%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20see%20whether%20that%20addition%20would%20elevate%20my%20sandwich.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20pickling%2C%20I%20followed%20this%20simple%20recipe%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thekitchn.com%2Fhow-to-make-quickpickled-red-onions-cooking-lessons-from-the-kitchn-193247%23post-recipe-10271%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Kitchn%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20dicing%20one%20red%20onion%20into%20small%20pieces%20and%20boiling%20water%20in%20my%20kettle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20filled%20a%20sealable%20glass%20jar%20with%20salt%2C%20sugar%2C%20and%20white%20vinegar%20and%20added%20a%20splash%20of%20boiling%20water%20to%20dissolve%20the%20mix%2C%20pouring%20the%20rest%20over%20the%20onions%20in%20a%20strainer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20transferred%20the%20onions%20to%20the%20glass%20jar%20and%20sealed%20it%2C%20leaving%20it%20at%20room%20temperature%20for%2030%20minutes%20before%20putting%20it%20in%20the%20fridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoasting%20the%20garlic%20took%20the%20longest%2C%20as%20it%20requires%20baking%20an%20oiled%20head%20of%20the%20ingredient%20in%20foil%20for%20about%2045%20minutes.%20But%20once%20I%20got%20that%20out%20of%20the%20way%2C%20the%20donkey%20sauce%20came%20together%20in%20no%20time%20and%20made%20a%20generous%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2270c13bee-cd76-4554-a8b7-8721bcee04b6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOnce%20the%20prep%20work%20was%20out%20of%20the%20way%2C%20I%20assembled%20my%20sandwich%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22guy%20fieri%20sandwich%20tips%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6081a4b94becb800190f68e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAssembling%20the%20sandwich%20was%20very%20easy.%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%20for%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20placed%20two%20slices%20of%20bread%20in%20the%20toaster%20oven%20because%2C%20according%20to%20Fieri%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20gotta%20toast%20it%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20good%20sandwich%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20wholeheartedly%20agree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20I%20cut%20thin%20slices%20of%20heirloom%20tomato%2C%20rinsed%20and%20dried%20my%20lettuce%2C%20and%20laid%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-vegan-roast-to-buy-for-holidays-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20meat%20alternative%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cheese%2C%20sauces%2C%20and%20pickled%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20pulled%20the%20warm%20bread%20out%2C%20I%20quickly%20spread%20brown%20mustard%20on%20one%20slice%20and%20donkey%20sauce%20on%20the%20other.%20I%20added%20the%20tomato%20and%20pickled%20ingredients%2C%20then%20the%20cheese%2C%20lettuce%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bturkey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22guy%20fieri%20sandwich%20tips%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6081a4e6354dde0018c06a83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20sandwich%20was%20stacked%20up%20quite%20taller%20than%20my%20usual%20lunches.%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%20for%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20meal%20was%20definitely%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%20much%20heftier%20than%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-not-to-do-when-making-a-sandwich-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etypical%20lunchtime%20sandwich%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20usually%20just%20has%20some%20hummus%2C%20cucumbers%2C%20tomato%2C%20lettuce%2C%20and%20maybe%20cheese%20and%20%26quot%3Bturkey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-best-way-to-cut-your-sandwich-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecut%20the%20bread%20diagonally%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20took%20a%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223bf7360f-bae0-4156-8185-f392e1176996%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFieri%20said%20he%20loves%20juxtaposition%2C%20and%20this%20sandwich%20delivers%20that%20in%20spades%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22guy%20fieri%20sandwich%20tips%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6081a5224becb800190f68e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20enjoyed%20nearly%20everything%20about%20this%20sandwich.%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%20for%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chef%20is%20a%20self-proclaimed%20%26quot%3Bjuxtaposition%20guy%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20it's%20fitting%20that%20this%20sandwich%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20contrasting%20components.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20the%20variety%20of%20textures%20and%20temperatures%2C%20as%20the%20cold%2C%20crisp%20lettuce%20and%20slightly%20soft%20tomato%20paired%20wonderfully%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-reviewed-one-of-the-most-reviewed-sandwich-shops-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewarm%20bread%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20crunchy%20veggies%2C%20and%20creamy%20sauce.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20the%20many%20flavor%20profiles%2C%20from%20the%20savory%20%26quot%3Bturkey%26quot%3B%20and%20cheese%20to%20the%20slightly%20sweet%20pickled%20onions%20and%20bread.%20I%20honestly%20could%20do%20without%20the%20giardiniera%2C%20but%20that%20wasn't%20surprising%20since%20I%20don't%20love%20carrots%20or%20cauliflower%2C%20especially%20on%20a%20sandwich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20the%20two%20sauces%2C%20juicy%20tomato%20slices%2C%20and%20pickled%20toppings%20that%20carried%20some%20moisture%2C%20the%20sandwich%20quickly%20got%20messy%20and%20started%20dripping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb8ec54a-6a50-4c78-a00a-fd6d7d6b273b%5C%22%3EFieri's%20tips%20changed%20my%20mindset%20about%20making%20sandwiches%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20I%20loved%20this%20more%20playful%20and%20experimental%20approach%20to%20making%20a%20sandwich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rarely%20venture%20past%20the%20basics%2C%20but%20these%20tips%20made%20me%20realize%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20elevate%20such%20a%20simple%20lunch%20by%20whipping%20up%20homemade%20sauces%20or%20adding%20pickled%20onions%20and%20jalape%C3%B1os.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20eating%20something%20basic%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20taking%20an%20easy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrying-guy-fieri-favorite-breakfast-dish-grits-recipe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrip%20to%20Flavortown%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20July%2023%2C%202021%2C%20and%20most%20recently%20updated%20on%20March%2012%2C%202026.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-for-making-perfect-sandwich-guy-fieri-easy-upgrades-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773331094000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6081a5644becb800190f68ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-for-making-perfect-sandwich-guy-fieri-easy-upgrades-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Celebrity%20chef%20Guy%20Fieri%20shared%20his%20favorite%20ways%20to%20upgrade%20a%20sandwich%20with%20tasty%20ingredients%20and%20easy%20tips%2C%20so%20I%20put%20his%20advice%20to%20the%20test.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Paige%20Bennett)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-for-making-perfect-sandwich-guy-fieri-easy-upgrades-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20A%20Family%20Dispute%20Is%20Shadowing%20Jaswant%20Singh%20Legacy%20In%20Rajasthan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22This%20family%20drama%20has%20gripped%20western%20Rajasthan%2C%20as%20it%20centers%20on%20the%20political%20legacy%20of%20Jaswant%20Singh%2C%20a%20nine-time%20MP%20and%20towering%20figure%20who%20served%20as%20India's%20Foreign%20and%20Finance%