0Aryan%20Brotherhood.%20The%20operation%20infiltrated%20chapters%20in%20northeast%20Ohio%20and%20western%20Pennsylvania%2C%20resulting%20in%20raids%20on%20June%2023%2C%202005.%20The%20raids%20led%20to%20the%20seizure%20of%20more%20than%2060%20weapons%2C%20including%2013%20fully%20automatic%20machine%20guns%2C%20and%20narcotics.%20Thirty-four%20members%20and%20associates%20of%20the%20Aryan%20Brotherhood%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20leaving%20ATF%20in%202014%2C%20D'Alesio%20became%20an%20owner%20of%20the%20Black%20River%20Tobacco%20Company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20more%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkschoolhouse.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewww.hkschoolhouse.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-outlaw-biker-gangs-actually-work-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773330961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9ac991fb3fcb42648f945%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-outlaw-biker-gangs-actually-work-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Frank%20D'Alesio%20spent%20nearly%20two%20decades%20embedded%20in%20investigations%20targeting%20outlaw%20motorcycle%20clubs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dibekwe%40businessinsider.com%20(David%20Ibekwe%2CJu%20Shardlow)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-outlaw-biker-gangs-actually-work-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20xAI%20exodus%3A%20Another%20cofounder%20gone%2C%20and%20one%20more%20has%20told%20people%20he's%20leaving%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20walking%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2b6c04d65ec517529e1f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221952%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMost%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20xAI%20cofounders%20have%20left%20the%20company.%3Cp%3EJosh%20Edelson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EZihang%20Dai%20left%20xAI%20this%20week%2C%20and%20Guodong%20Zhang%20is%20expected%20to%20depart%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20insiders%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EZhang%20oversaw%20the%20company's%20coding%20agent%20and%20its%20video%20and%20image%20generation%20tool.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20the%20departures%2C%20only%20two%20of%20the%20engineers%20who%20cofounded%20the%20company%20with%20Elon%20Musk%20will%20remain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exodus%20of%20cofounders%20from%20Elon%20Musk's%20AI%20startup%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZihang%20Dai%20left%20xAI%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%20His%20xAI%20badge%20has%20vanished%20from%20his%20X%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Guodong%20Zhang%20has%20told%20people%20he%20plans%20to%20leave%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20insiders%20said.%20His%20X%20profile%20still%20has%20an%20xAI%20badge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20follows%20the%20recent%20exits%20of%20a%20string%20of%20xAI%20cofounders%2C%20including%20Toby%20Pohlen%2C%20Jimmy%20Ba%2C%20Tony%20Wu%2C%20and%20Greg%20Yang%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20have%20left%20since%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Dai%20and%20Zhang%20depart%2C%20only%20two%20of%20the%2011%20people%20who%20started%20the%20company%20with%20Musk%20in%202023%20%E2%80%94%20Manuel%20Kroiss%20and%20Ross%20Nordeen%20%E2%80%94%20will%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhang%20reports%20directly%20to%20Musk%20and%20led%20two%20of%20the%20company's%20key%20projects%3A%20Grok%20Code%20and%20Grok%20Imagine.%20He%20was%20given%20a%20larger%20role%20at%20xAI%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20shortly%20before%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-loses-cofounder-tony-wu-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWu%20left%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20company%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Musk%20told%20the%20Abundance%20Conference%20that%20%26quot%3BGrok%20is%20currently%20behind%20in%20coding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20I%20was%20late%20for%20this%20was%20that%20I%20was%20just%20in%20a%20giant%20sort%20of%20all-hands%20on%20coding%2C%20going%20through%20all%20the%20things%20that%20need%20to%20happen%20to%20essentially%20exceed%20our%20competitors%20on%20coding%2C%20which%20I%20think%20we'll%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20joining%20xAI%2C%20Zhang%20worked%20at%20Google%20DeepMind%20and%20received%20his%20Ph.D.%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Toronto%2C%20according%20to%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDai%20was%20a%20member%20of%20technical%20staff%20at%20the%20company.%20He%20worked%20at%20Google%20and%20received%20a%20Ph.D.%20in%20Computer%20Science%20at%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University%20prior%20to%20helping%20found%20xAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReached%20by%20phone%2C%20Zhang%20and%20Dai%20declined%20to%20comment.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20xAI%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXAI%20just%20hired%20Jason%20Ginsberg%20and%20Andrew%20Milich%2C%20who%20together%20led%20product%20engineering%20at%20AI%20coding%20company%20Cursor%2C%20they%20announced%20on%20X%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Musk%20made%20clear%20in%20a%20reply%20to%20a%20X%20post%20about%20the%20new%20hires%20that%20he%20thinks%20xAI%20needed%20a%20shake-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BxAI%20was%20not%20built%20right%20first%20time%20around%2C%20so%20is%20being%20rebuilt%20from%20the%20foundations%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BSame%20thing%20happened%20with%20Tesla.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20shed%20dozens%20of%20employees%20since%20January.%20Musk%20announced%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-all-hands-new-structure-recording-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereorganized%20xAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%20and%20parted%20ways%20with%20some%20staffers%20as%20a%20result.%20Some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-leadership-style-big-year-grok-ipo-spacex-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecuts%20have%20impacted%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20company's%20AI%20white%20collar%20project%2C%20Macrohard%2C%20and%20Grok%20Imagine%2C%20its%20AI%20image%20and%20video%20generator%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20we've%20reached%20a%20certain%20scale%2C%20we're%20organizing%20the%20company%20to%20be%20more%20effective%20at%20this%20scale.%20And%20actually%2C%20when%20this%20happens%2C%20there's%20some%20people%20who%20are%20better%20suited%20for%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20a%20company%20and%20less%20suited%20for%20the%20later%20stages%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20during%20the%20February%20all-hands%20event%2C%20which%20was%20later%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhang%20is%20one%20of%20a%20handful%20of%20xAI%20leaders%20who%20presented%20at%20the%20all-hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reorganization%20took%20place%20shortly%20after%20two%20of%20Musk's%20direct%20reports%2C%20Wu%20and%20Ba%2C%20left%20the%20company%20and%20xAI%20was%20acquired%20by%20Musk's%20rocket%20company%2C%20SpaceX.%20The%20company%20is%20reportedly%20gearing%20up%20for%20an%20initial%20public%20offering%20this%20year%20that%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-would-earn-google-111-billion-as-an-early-investor-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evalue%20SpaceX%20at%20%241.5%20trillion.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20three%20weeks%20after%20the%20reorg%2C%20Pohlen%2C%20who%20led%20Macrohard%2C%20announced%20he'd%20left%20the%20company.%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20this%20week%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F